  <sect1>
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      Welcome to the Slack World website! The Slack World is a monthly
      <ulink url="http://www.slackware.com/">Slackware Linux</ulink> 
      magazine. The main aim of the project is to fill a few gaps that
      we see in covering Slackware-related information by other resources,
      by providing in-depth articles and a summary of recent Slackware-related
      news.
    </para>

    <para>
      We are currently working on the first issue, please stay tuned!
    </para>

